]] analysis fails

test duplicate field name 2 [[
  {x = 1, x = {y = 2} }
]] analysis fails

test duplicate record field extension 1 [[
  {x = 2} extends {x = 1}
]] analysis succeeds

test duplicate record field extension 2 [[
